  "title": "*NEW* 1 year Maintenance / Facilities Coordinator ($3000 to $4200) #NJA",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Job: </strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative support to maintain accurate records of maintenance, repairs, and inspections</li></ul><ul><li>Coordinate communications between internal teams and external contractors for facility services, ensuring quality, cost-effectiveness, timely delivery, and safety compliance</li><li>Assist the Maintenance Supervisor in conducting safety inspections and preparing related reports</li><li>Support routine maintenance inspections and follow-up actions</li><li>Oversee contractor activities including installation, maintenance, and project execution</li></ul><p><strong>The Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 2 years of relevant experience in facilities maintenance</li><li>NTC/ITE in Engineering or equivalent</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Interested applicants can send their detailed resumes to </strong><a href=\"mailto:janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg </a><strong>or call JANE @ 6735 1955. </strong></p><p><strong>JANE LUI JIE'EN </strong></p><p><strong>CEI: R1104482</strong></p><p><u><strong>Company Reg. No. 199601303W || EA Licence No. 99C4599</strong></u></p>",
